                <h1>Understanding General Discharge: Key Facts & Implications</h1>
                <p>General discharge refers to the release of a service member from active duty, characterized by less than honorable reasons. This type of discharge can affect various benefits and job opportunities in the civilian sector. Understanding the implications is crucial for transitioning smoothly into civilian life.</p>
